features: LARGE CAPACITY BAKING BASKET: Are you worried that the air fryer tray doesn't have enough space? No problem now, our new upgraded large capacity tray measures 18.9"*13.1", which is equivalent to 2-3 regular trays. Plenty of cooking space for a large family's gourmet needs

SUPERIOR PERFORMANCE: The air fryer basket is made of high quality food grade 304 stainless steel, BPA free and FDA compliant; the air fryer basket for oven is safe to use at temperatures up to 450°F, warp resistant and non-deformable; the nonstick coating on the surface releases food easily, which makes cleanup a breeze and saves you a lot of valuable time

LESS FAT AND CALORIES: No or less oil or butter required. The oven air fryer basket and tray set design allows it to catch excess fat, which means you can enjoy your favorite fried foods without having to worry about adding calories and fat. So you can cook crispy, healthy fried foods with less oil, while retaining their original flavor and nutrition

360° CIRCULATION HEATING: The air fryer rack is designed with an ultra-fine mesh basket that circulates heat 360° to ensure food is heated evenly, so you don't need to turn or rotate your food while it's cooking. Air circulation reduces the chance of food burning and provides a perfect golden brown surface every time you bake

MULTI-PURPOSE BAKING BASKET: The air fryer basket for oven meets all kitchen needs. Perfect for baking homemade pizzas, chicken nuggets, sandwiches, chips and more. Ideal for everyday cooking, family dinners, friends gatherings, holiday celebrations and more. We offer 24-hour friendly service and one-year warranty promise, if you have any problem with the product you received, please contact us promptly and we will solve it for you at the first time!

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: JOYCUBE 18.9" × 13.1" LARGE AIR FRYER BASKET FOR OVEN Get delectable results! Are you worried that the air fryer basket doesn't have enough space? No problem now, our new upgraded large capacity oven tray measures 18.9"*13.1", which is equivalent to 2-3 regular trays. Plenty of cooking space for a large family's gourmet needs! KEY FEATURES: - Nonstick surface releases food easily - Oven-safe to 450 °F - Stainless steel heats evenly - Dishwasher safe for easy clean-up

NONSTICK OVEN AIR FRYER BASKET AND TRAY The nonstick oven air fryer basket and tray makes it easy to bake all your favorite cakes and cookies with confidence. Constructed with heavy-stainless steel, designed to brown even the most delicate cookies evenly, making them hardworking kitchen tools for years to come. The interlocking nonstick layers deliver high performance release, minimizing broken cookies and stuck-on baked goods. Also for quick & effortless food release plus it does not emit any weird odor or smell.

HOW TO CARE FOR NONSTICK BAKEWARE Allow baking pan to cool before cleaning. Never immerse hot bakeware in cold water. While bakeware sets are dishwasher safe, hand washing using a liquid dishwashing detergent and a nonabrasive cleaning sponge will keep your bakeware looking better longer

reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars I was happy and then I was sad.
reviews.reviewText: The set looks slick and modern. After my first use I placed it into the dishwasher. Some oil and burnt bits didn’t come off after the wash so I took some soapy water and tried to scrap it off and the black enamel came off! Now my tray has spots missing the black coating. That was disappointing. Also it did rust a lil while in the dishwasher but I was able to clean it off. Basically it has not lived up to it’s production description.

reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Fits perfectly in Breville Pro BUT has already visible scratches
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I just received and opened this, it came well packaged and both pieces were wrapped in bubble bags. The tray already have visible and deep scratches on it. You can also tell that the coatings came off from those scratches. Too bad for that, cause I like the matte coating and that it fits perfectly in my Breville air fryer. But my purpose for this is to keep the tray in to protect the bottom and heating elements of air fryer from drippings. This looks like it will be a disposable one for my purpose since durability is questionable.
